com.mysema.query.sql.codegen

Interface NamingStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNamingStrategy, DefaultNamingStrategy, ExtendedNamingStrategy, OriginalNamingStrategy

    public interface NamingStrategy
    NamingStrategy defines a conversion strategy from table to class and column to property names
    Author:
    tiwe
